<abstract>
On the day of the Epiphany, the church of Araceli removes the Christ child from the manger of its nativity scene. The effigy is presented three times at the church's entrance, each time blessing the throngs that have gathered for benediction. [pp 1-2] [Translated and paraphrased by SR]
</abstract>
